*Pijan* čovek je bio u pravu. (The drunk man was right.)

*Pijana* devojka je pala sa stolice. (The drunk girl fell off the chair.)

Kafana je bila puna *pijanih* ljudi. (The bar was full of drunk people.)

*Pišan* konobar je otišao ranije. (The tipsy waiter left earlier.)

Ona je bila *pijana* od sreće. (She was drunk with joy.)